Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan's charm offensive
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w54w
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Nov 1980
President-elect Reagan wins over Washington with his charm offensive. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less